# JIRA Admin Plugin

Simple Jira Plugin which allows Sys Admin to change its configuration using dedicated section in Admin/Application

Features:
 - Admin Configuration page is implemented both as Servlet and Actions (so there are two separate pages allowing to change same settings)
 - Read only page for simple user (Admin and Non-Admin)
 - Simple REST interface (accessible at /rest/tutorial-plugin/1.0/) which returns the parameter values
 - Using AUI
 
